{"tid":2379301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【封區過後】小店東主嘆損失慘重　冀政府補償　「講咩過年呀，過身就有！」","createTime":"2021-01-25T06:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T07:36:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"75d1e6d1dfc21ac4116930925e7122e7d808f0d6","tid":2379301,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:51:52.000Z","msg":"油麻地佐敦四街「封區」48 小時，至今晨 4 時終解封，惟今早仍有大批身穿白色保護衣的工作人員在各大廈門外駐守，有區內包點店店主羅先生表示，街道上「白衣人」比市民更多，「邊個夠膽嚟食嘢啊？咪又係做唔到生意」，更稱「仲講咩過年呀，過身就有！」但亦有魚檔檔主認為，檢測能找出染病者，避免進一步傳播病毒，「叫做好過無囉」。<br />\n<br />\n在上海街經營蒸包店 8 年的羅先生憶述，兩日前凌晨 4 時，正下樓準備開店，突然被禁止離開大廈，只能回家，「自己鬧自己抵死，點解要係油麻地開鋪？」他批評政府公布安排不理想，「你封唔緊要，早啲通知嘛」，「兩日唔開，人工損失、鋪租損失、貨錢損失，都有成萬蚊」。即使該區今日已解封，惟區內仍有白色保護衣工作人員駐守，「白衣人仲多過普通人，邊個夠膽嚟食嘢啊？咪又係做唔到生意」，羅先生又質疑食環署人員為何要待今早才清潔洗地，「解封前唔洗，點解係要等人哋開舖開工先嚟洗？」<br />\n<br />\n他表示在疫情下本身生意已欠佳，「而家直情係雪上加霜 、靜上加靜」，擔心捱不到過年，「仲講咩過年呀，過身就有」、「無希望啦，得絕望」。他期望政府可以「補償多少」，「當係可憐下我哋小商戶啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8C-%E5%B0%8F%E5%BA%97%E6%9D%B1%E4%B8%BB%E5%98%86%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%E6%85%98%E9%87%8D-%E5%86%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%A3%9C%E5%84%9F-%E8%AC%9B%E5%92%A9%E9%81%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%91%80-%E9%81%8E%E8%BA%AB%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2598%2586%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2585%2598%25E9%2587%258D-%25E5%2586%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%25A3%259C%25E5%2584%259F-%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%2592%25A9%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2591%2580-%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%259C%2589%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=809222f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2598%2586%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2585%2598%25E9%2587%258D-%25E5%2586%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%25A3%259C%25E5%2584%259F-%25E8%25AC%259B%25E5%2592%25A9%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2591%2580-%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%259C%2589%2F&h=c5788b5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%81%E5%8D%80%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8C-%E5%B0%8F%E5%BA%97%E6%9D%B1%E4%B8%BB%E5%98%86%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%E6%85%98%E9%87%8D-%E5%86%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%A3%9C%E5%84%9F-%E8%AC%9B%E5%92%A9%E9%81%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%91%80-%E9%81%8E%E8%BA%AB%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89/</a>"},{"pid":"1bbd452f17ceb6772a992b81b88af4d7818e805b","tid":2379301,"uid":78243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"國安又要拉人"},{"pid":"99f2ed5218670d70d072643959ada833e01745f7","tid":2379301,"uid":342823,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"唔做幾日生意就損失慘重, 你係一樓一我就信.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd65c72992a76548c10b59be22e9abc03aaebea","tid":2379301,"uid":2959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:55:55.000Z","msg":"連登: 做生意包賺咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5609a5349faa9371fbcd49028426f8a44c0a408d","tid":2379301,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"99f2ed5218670d70d072643959ada833e01745f7","tid":2379301,"uid":342823,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"唔做幾日生意就損失慘重, 你係一樓一我就信.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" 